e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:00:37.000Z","msg":"國家安全為重中之重，不容外部勢力說三道四"},{"pid":"8cc5b99bae024a2e8b85120079a1951810aa14c0","tid":2195534,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a2e66ce44babd7f95a2dbd0d40aa91a5d337d4a","tid":2195534,"uid":183758,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T08:47:05.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">支共你嘅結局只有死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:01:25.000Z","msg":"澳洲終於肯做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}